- [P0] Phase 3 remaining: SD subscribe/ack flow, event→eventgroup mapping
- [P0] Phase 4 remaining: reflection-based auto-generation from annotated service structs
- [P0] Phase 5: E2E protection + Security policies — DONE
- [P1] Phase 5: E2E protection + Security policies — DONE
